From: Joerg Roedel <jroedel@suse.de>
Date: Wed, 29 Apr 2020 15:36:57 +0200
Subject: iommu/s390: Convert to probe/release_device() call-backs
Git-commit: 522af649e57b3e3a347a8261f609f73ab4143f20
Patch-mainline: v5.8-rc1
References: bsc#1175713

Convert the S390 IOMMU driver to use the probe_device() and
release_device() call-backs of iommu_ops, so that the iommu core code
does the group and sysfs setup.

Signed-off-by: Joerg Roedel <jroedel@suse.de>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/20200429133712.31431-20-joro@8bytes.org
Signed-off-by: Joerg Roedel <jroedel@suse.de>
---
